:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare:::

Ramjet: Yes, I am the leader of the Destrocons. At first when we came to 
earth- a while ago- we were Alliance members, but Zardus had no use for us, 
so we took off and joined the Destrons. My team and i have been loyal 
Destrons ever since, and if you want strength, Skywarp, Dirge and I combine 
to form the giant Destructus.  The other two, Falcon and Snare, were created 
as Neocons, but their leader died and they left to join the Destrons.  Now 
the Neocon base is destroyed, but together we can fix it and use it. My team 
and I are ready to go if you are.
::With that he and the other two Destrocons transform to beast mode.  Falcon 
and Snare transform to their jet modes, and Falcon, being the largest of the 
two, opened his cockpit::
Falcon: Hop in.
::They see the Alliance bots coming::
Ramjet: Us? Hmm.  What do you think Cygnar?

--part1_4d.851424f.27d6a1bf_boundary
